Reasoning: The paper deals with the problem of automatic checkout using computer vision technology in the retail industry. Therefore, it is most likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also proposes a new dataset and benchmarks the performance of various approaches, which suggests that it could also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves image retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL) tasks, which could also be relevant sub-categories.
